            "text": "Just water for now.",
            "translation": "فعلاً فقط آب."
        },
        {
            "order": 10,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Okay. Your food will be ready soon.",
            "translation": "باشه. غذایتان به‌زودی آماده می‌شود."
        },
        {
            "order": 11,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Thank you. We are very hungry.",
